# A380X API Hinweise

A380X Presets (FBW):
- `A32NX_AIRCRAFT_PRESET_LOAD` (1..5) + `A32NX_AIRCRAFT_PRESET_LOAD_PROGRESS` (0..1)
- `A32NX_LOAD_AIRCRAFT_PRESET` (1..5) + `A32NX_LOAD_AIRCRAFT_PRESET_PROGRESS` (0..1)

Siehe FBW A380X Systems API / Flight Deck API:
https://docs.flybywiresim.com/aircraft/a380x/a380x-api/a380x-systems-api/
